summary: This mod turns the Sea of Ghosts (and the rest of the seas in Skyrim and Solstheim) into a lively Sea of Spirits by adding many new sea creatures, like whales, narwhals, sharks, dreugh, and many others. Essentially just a "sea creatures-only" version of our Beasts of Tamriel mod without any of the land creatures.
